    <Speaker>
        <SpeakerInfo>
            <div>
                <ab class="ab_indent">zōt ud rāspīg <em>sastica</em>, zōt <em>vaṇtāca</em>... vid. Nērangs.</ab>
            </div>
        </SpeakerInfo>
    </Speaker>
    <Apparatus>
        <Critical/>
        <Commentary/>
        <RecitationInstruction>
            <ab>YR15.1a <em>sastica vaṇtāca</em>...] <em>sastaca</em> OD <em>ahurəm mazdą̇m</em> (YR16.1) 320; <em>vaṇtāca</em> OD OL Y <em>ahurəm mazdąm</em> (YR16.1) 300, 360, 370.</ab>
        </RecitationInstruction>
    </Apparatus>
    <Parallels/>
    <Ritual>
        <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
            <ab>YR15.1 (mss. 300, 360, 370):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                <em>sastica</em> bē gōwišn ud bōy ō ī ātaxš dahišn datuš bē abrāzēnišn (Paz. <em>dārəṣ̌n</em> 360, 370) pas <em>vaṇtāca</em> tā ō ī <em>ahurəm</em></ab> 
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "They have to recite <em>sastica</em>. (The <em>rāspīg</em>) has to give <em>bōy</em> to the fire and (the <em>zōt</em>) has to raise the <em>datuš</em> and then 
                (to recite) <em>vaṇtāca</em> until <em>ahurəm</em>."</ab>
        </Nerangs>
    </Ritual>
